### Sample API Requests for Banking Transactions API
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ===== TRANSACTION ENDPOINTS =====

### 1. Create a new DEPOSIT transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-99999",
  "amount": 500.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "DEPOSIT"
}

### 2. Create a new TRANSFER transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 250.75,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "TRANSFER"
}

### 3. Create a new WITHDRAWAL transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "WITHDRAWAL"
}

### 4. Test invalid transaction (negative amount)
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": -100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "TRANSFER"
}

### 5. Test invalid currency
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "XXX",
  "type": "TRANSFER"
}

### 6. Get all transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions

### 7. Get transactions for specific account
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345

### 8. Get transactions by type
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?type=TRANSFER

### 9. Get transactions by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?from=2024-01-01T00:00:00&to=2024-12-31T23:59:59

### 10. Get transactions with multiple filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345&type=TRANSFER

### 11. Get transaction by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/{{transactionId}}

### ===== ACCOUNT ENDPOINTS =====

### 12. Get account balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-12345/balance

### 13. Get account summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-12345/summary

### 14. Get another account balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-67890/balance

### 15. Get another account summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-67890/summary
